      <title>中国顶级汽车经销商考虑债务到期后的还款方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/china-s-top-car-dealer-mulls-repayment-options-as-debt-matures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最大的汽车经销商之一正在与银行家合作，探讨其美元债券即将到期的还款方案，这突显出现金困境正在蔓延到境况不佳的房地产行业之外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/china-s-top-car-dealer-mulls-repayment-options-as-debt-matures</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 07:51:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
