      <title>印度法院取消提前释放古吉拉特邦轮奸犯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/india-court-cancels-early-release-of-bilkis-bano-gang-rape-case-convicts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最高法院撤销了提前释放 11 名被判无期徒刑的男子的决定，这些男子在 2002 年西部古吉拉特邦的社区骚乱中被判轮奸和谋杀罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/india-court-cancels-early-release-of-bilkis-bano-gang-rape-case-convicts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 07:51:40 GMT</pubDate>
