      <title>瑞士通胀加速，但仍保持在瑞士央行目标范围内</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/swiss-inflation-quickens-but-stays-well-within-snb-target-range</link>
      <description><![CDATA[12 月份瑞士通胀增速超出预期，这可能是通胀回升的开始，未来几个月的物价压力将更大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/swiss-inflation-quickens-but-stays-well-within-snb-target-range</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
